channel.title: Fast the slow torrent speed
channel.description: Well I was downloading a movie and it was up around 200 kb/s. I had to shut down my computer so I stoped downloading it. When I came back to download it again it wouldn't get higher then 10 kb/s. So I'm just wondering wtf is going on?

item.title: Fast the slow torrent speed
item.dc:creator: @Schizzo Schizzo
item.description:
@Schizzo wrote:

It could also be that the primary seeders simply stopped uploading. Just leave it over night or something, if you really want the movie that bad.
